性能也更为出色。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t2101/185/792456567/205638/453bb31d/5629a658Na56a4d58.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; top: 760px; left: 50px; width: 540px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">高通骁龙四核64位处理器，搭配2GB运行内存，令A33运行非常流畅。快速启动应用程序，游戏畅玩不卡顿，多个APP也能同时运行。16GB大内存，能轻松容纳2000+首高品质音乐*，或3400+张高清图片*。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t2101/182/762508627/77538/8cb98dfa/5629a65aN10e255f2.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; top: 250px; left: 50px; width: 610px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">灵敏度更高，帧率更高，有效减少噪点，让拍照与视频通话时画质更清晰。配合美颜3.0与绚彩滤镜，每一张自拍都更加动人。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img12.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t2149/164/781593440/138893/337cb97e/5629a65aN68cf4293.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; top: 210px; left: 50px; width: 540px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A33拥有美颜3.0，你只需随手一拍，无需繁琐的二次修图，浑然天成的自拍美照即刻完成。独特的夜拍补光模式，让你在暗光环境下，依然明亮动人。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t2155/188/794629175/56297/41b9b9af/5629a65bNe6063dab.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; top: 240px; left: 50px; width: 650px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">高达1.4um的大像素，让800万像素后置镜头的效果媲美相机。采用背照式设计，进光量更大，感光度更高，拍照更有质感。即使在暗光下，夜间自动补光功能也提升画质。从此，出门不再带相机，只需带上A33。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img10.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t2248/210/753354895/187327/c900765b/5629a65cN32684786.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; top: 220px; left: 50px; width: 400px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">我们通过建立声学模型，对耳机输出提供音质补偿，实现低、中、高音的更好平衡。打造更贴合A33的悦耳音质，每一首歌都值得细细回味。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t2407/87/2131887285/124109/87be4cf9/56988f7cN26f0f381.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; top: 210px; left: 50px; width: 640px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ColorOS 2.1经过不断打磨完善，启动更快、滑动更流畅、系统更稳定、内存占用更小；崭新的视觉设计，重绘所有图标和界面，简约大气。在新的Android 5.1系统上，实现更优的内存管控和续航管理。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t2383/164/767389669/70199/882802e3/5629a65dN055d913e.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; top: 210px; left: 50px; width: 640px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">你可以随意控制联网权限，提前预设流量开关状态，不用担心流氓应用偷跑流量。使用流量上网时，根据需求对文字和图片进行云服务压缩，流量一省再省。</p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img13.360buyimg.com/cms/jfs/t1966/176/771601550/84365/449dc4d9/5629a65eNde0465eb.jpg\"/> \r\n &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/jfs/t4372/18/117254409/133954/71ab6913/58af9f1eN083192fc.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '0');
